Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Neo Nazis are trying to burn down the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Turkish woman had already been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be arriving shortly at the place indicated by Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to use a gun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Frankfurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to Calvin Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to kill Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure General Wolf will be disappointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since after acknowledging your skills, he \N commissioned you to eliminate Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commissioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody commissions me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill Johan of my own volition!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go to Calvin Street for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:35.80,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,188)\pos(359,309)}Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just received word that preparations for the fire are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This celebration of our superior race must \N be wreathed in glorious flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people like them even in a superior race.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is a thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he tried to inform the Turkish people about our actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must purify them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we are going to burn this place down anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.  Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your mom will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ay...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter gave me some general directions, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are that Tenma guy he was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came here, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what about Ayse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ayse's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her son in her arms again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this child going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is still so small, and now he doesn't \N have his mother anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone else become a victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the town leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Setting fire to the town, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fascists have been threatening to do that all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't keep wasting our time with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this Japanese person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is even more suspicious that he showed up \N here, even though he is being chased himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse died because of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was killed because she tried \N to warn you all about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayse was a hooker like yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is normal for people to go missing after doing \N business with the Germans in that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a disgrace to the Turkish people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows whose child that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You especially should know that we all \N do what we need to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to live, please listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you all burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking us to become vigilantes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try doing what this Japanese man proposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Deniz...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to listen to this suspicious Japanese person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is indeed suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are Japanese that can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like General Nogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General... Nogi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  You don't know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, a Japanese general named Nogi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:06:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...saved Turkish navy men when they \N were stranded in the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble all the men in town!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's dinner seems special!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait.  Don't be in such a rush to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else you will finish eating before show time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time the main course is served, the \N show should be reaching its climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we taste the '76 Chateau Latour that \N I've specially ordered for this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then wrap our tongues around \N my favorite, raw halibut caviar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, as we do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!  The first fire has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is merely an appetizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is the main course?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to rush, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just enjoy the meal and \N gaze upon the show with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the main course?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that fire is just an appetizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to burn for the main course?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water!  Bring more water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough fire extinguishers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't all go in at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who is not doing anything, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the fire did start upwind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means this side will be in danger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Split up into three groups!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.  Yet another beautiful guest \N has joined me for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll really shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just put that dangerous thing away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?  We will enjoy this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, your appetizer is disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was just an appetizer, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is your favorite, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we enjoy this moment together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this festival is about accepting \N your brother as a member of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not what Johan wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the place he indicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan didn't wish for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't wish for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.  Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed Ayse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do any more awful things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the main course?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of town are you going to set on fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are setting fire to places the fire trucks can't get to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the injured out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a guy who said he saw a boy who looked \N like him in the park this afternoon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not going to chase her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue on with the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder she is Johan's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her eyes just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really was willing to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I almost told her \N where the real main course is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we continue with your dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, bring me a change of underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a very frightening girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, miss, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you guys...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is all that brat's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'm outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way they are gonna stop \N with these simple little fires!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about it since I used to live \N in this town when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was gonna burn this town down...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wouldn't set fire to a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying this place was just a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three places upwind have all been put out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe you one, Mr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, it didn't turn serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must treat the injured first!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let there be any more victims...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by a decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The direction of the wind is gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time every night, the wind stops for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, a breeze starts blowing in off the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is finally time for the main course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we have a toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to rest, since you are injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be so strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, the town didn't have any major fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those fascists are probably pissed \N that the fire isn't spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn't underestimate us Turks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were the other injured people taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mosque by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a break and have something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treating the injured comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the fires have only been decoys so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then where are they going to set the real fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what happens to a town like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I have something to take  care of first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were you, where would you set the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The breeze will be coming in off the river shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you set the fire to the abandoned \N factory by the river, it would be all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be enough chemicals left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time for the main course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, sate my hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is proceeding accordingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time for the festival of the superior race.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to put out the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise to Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.  This is the warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they didn't know about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these all the chemicals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this many chemicals went up in flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the town would be done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll protect this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let them set this place on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I slipped...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gasoline...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:14:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is okay.  I can walk by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just go to the shelter over there \N and I'll take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sprained it while trying to save \N some important heirlooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have this carpet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't need this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,800,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is a first rate item worth \N at least 1,000,000 Marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Dieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, where did Dieter go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh!  The kid went to the abandoned \N factory by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Factory...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, the breeze will blow in off the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the chemicals in the factory catch fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this town will be finished
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, this is the breeze I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell everyone at the shelter \N to get away from the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Heckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are Johan's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw away the lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I start a fire, the gasoline will ignite...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...And this warehouse will instantly \N become a sea of flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot you in the head before that can happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I sever your cranial nerves...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can stop you from moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been training for half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this distance, I'm a perfect shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not be intimidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the festival for the superior race.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is to accept Johan as a member of our group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan doesn't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan did come to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he killed one of your leaders \N and his subordinates, then left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A message?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not the type of person you think he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is more more complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is much more frightening than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is... writhing in pain, in an abyss of grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, I hope you don't get on their bad side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.   Haven't you had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to let Dieter die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine, I'll tell you!  I'll tell you, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said your friend's name was Tenma, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone named Tenma, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really a brave man, also?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't want him to fire a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want him to kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should never kill anyone either, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how bad the person is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do what I'm about to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heckel, put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The carpet!  Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... 1,000,000 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!  It is the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that man to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a boat by the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and run, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main course...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...got cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please come to the \N station for a more detailed..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina, promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not shoot people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Johan's message!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going there right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I shot Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I finally figured out why he wanted \N me to shoot him in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...isn't alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two Johans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why... it is not your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...aim at Johan's head, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's quit wasting our time here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I can't take this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I still had that carpet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Help me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The monster inside me is about to explode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, inside Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are two personalities?
